## Changelog
### Features
* 6f26e685f5bb653dc08f51543276fcedf09c66ed feat: Remove 1Password SDK integration
* fbdedfbd178d55c63ec1a5e7cc58766190e1f573 feat: Complete --progress and --working-tree option args
* 6b013c78ee463e4a5af027ea7483c1ace88693bb feat: Prevent inapplicable filename positional arguments
* c56a27daed931d7f8fc748e54227e8eb8c3da9c8 feat: Set LESS and LV env vars the same way that git does
### Fixes
* af5b03a56987f09d2d445497e8086edc2e285347 fix: Remove default submission when nothing is selected during promptMultichoice
* dc97563a557485badf58beb9849f0c32f80a4f35 fix: Doc on declaratve package installation
### Documentation updates
* 443e12d70440d45dcbe346b57fe189d4ab1a3825 docs: Add note on templates in edit command
* 0a04e76e3769e7fad13aa72b7d765f8fe6098e96 docs: Update docs for using delta
* 882696f778d1e186d17cf9460a14e77d601a6d21 docs: Remove unnecessary `--no-lock` Brew option
name: v2.61.0
